{"tid":1277914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年入境署放火燒死兩人，又係唔見係踐踏法治破壞一國兩制？","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T13:38:56.000Z","uid":77905,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"65416dc920ea98d346c5b248d90f9e0a689fe92b","tid":1277914,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"19年前發生的入境處縱火案釀成2死44傷更轟動全城，案中主腦施君龍被判謀殺罪成，後改判誤殺，服刑5年便出獄，更於2011年獲批單程證來港。<br />\n<br />\n2000年8月，24歲的施君龍與一批爭取居港權的內地人於灣仔入境事務大樓1301室示威，當時施曾對入境處職員指「出年今日係你哋死忌」，並揚言要將入境處職員「變燒豬」。<br />\n<br />\n其間有人淋天拿水及點火，42歲高級入境主任梁錦光及26歲示威者林小星被燒死。<br />\n<br />\n當年又唔見班親中屌撚屌撚佢地唔理性？"},{"pid":"5f71ba6fff5c59786b2bf9dd4122e5a5ea4a40a0","tid":1277914,"uid":77905,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"取消單程證！"},{"pid":"591f2e9b28ff674e7edaf4f7b19da16ef782ccc4","tid":1277914,"uid":34869,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"燒死兩件先5年<br />\n<br />\n天琦咁就6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1d16a480b78e6d2c4725a6b7d97f4dbcd8ceff","tid":1277914,"uid":77905,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"呢幾日示威者只係和平抗爭，所謂暴力傾向只係打爛玻璃。全世界都支持用和平手段，咁都叫暴力？"},{"pid":"77e8f11a582192641fcdf6fd277a21672724c5d6","tid":1277914,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3cf51c576afe0c1b1c3ef2f2e758337d52572e","tid":1277914,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj